channel.title: Help with Port Forwarding? (pics)
channel.description:
Ok so I have finished making my server and I cant log into it and neither can others and im pretty sure that its because I probably messed up on Portforwarding. (I have a D-link model DI-524 router). Ok so when im doing the portforwarding here is the pic of what I put in on my router:
When I'm putting in the portforwarding this is what it looks like:
[IMG]http://i628.photobucket.com/albums/uu3/Dzhambik6/privateserverhelp10-1.jpg[/img]
Now when I'm done with the Portforwarding I start up the server and it looks like this: (All looks good right?)
[IMG]http://i628.photobucket.com/albums/uu3/Dzhambik6/privateserverhelp11-1.jpg[/img]
Now Finally when I try to log in it looks like this: (I put in the server ip in file but I didn't show it because it would be advertising)
[IMG]http://i628.photobucket.com/albums/uu3/Dzhambik6/privateserverhelp12-1.jpg[/img]
Does anybody know how to fix this? if you can do it for me over teamviewer add me on msn: (Stefan_nba_Allstar@hotmail.com)
Thanks.
